div.div:
After being sealed away for 1,000 years, the War God Duan Yuxian has come back to a world that has forgotten him and his malevolent past. As he wanders aimlessly through the central plains ruled by the martial world, he comes across a dying little girl named Xiaomei and revives her out of pity. Although they try to live in peace as a family, the factions of the martial world refuse to let them be. Now, Duan Yuxian has no other choice but to remind them that the War God has truly returned.
(Source: Tapas)

Yeon Hwicheon from the Yeon Sect is deceived by the Dam Sect, who are after his sect's divine treasures, into an arranged marriage. Despite the unsightly scar on his face, he meets his kind-hearted wife, Dam Hwayeon, and they live a trouble-free life.
However, the Dam Sect, revealing their true intentions, causing the downfall of the Yeon Sect. He barely escapes and finds refuge in a cave. Here, he has a fateful encounter, through which he finds advanced martial arts skills.
Yeon Hwicheon finds himself regressing back to the moment right after his marriage. Yeon Hwicheon and the now stronger Yeon Sect quickly become the targets of the martial arts world, and Hwicheon, already aware of this, further elevates the martial arts of his sect and boldly throws down a challenge to the entire martial arts community under his name.
(Source: KakaoPage, translated)
